{
  "stem": "11797.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They used to pull down, take them-- show them with the [INAUDIBLE] what they call it in Jewish, no.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wear a little- under their clothes, they used to wear some kind of, like a little tallith, no.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they used to take off your jacket.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Show the world what you are.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You're very pious, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Show me your payos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they used to cut it off, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With my own eyes, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I felt-- I felt sorry for these people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I never knew that people of a high cultural society, which I learned in school, could-- could commit this kind of atrocities, this kind of shameful thing, to other people.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I always heard, when I was in school, that good piano players and good musicians were Germans.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Good learners.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "People, before the war, used to go to Germany to become doctors.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was afraid, when am I-- when they're going to come to me?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not now, not then, but eventually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually, I was in line, too.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father was-- he didn't have no work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, of course, no, right away-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] my father was-- was very-- he didn't know what to do, because there was no work, you know.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and right away they performed-- they had-- they-- they blocked off the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They blocked off-- made a ghetto out of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took all the Jews from other sections, who lived in non-Jewish neighborhoods, no, and they put them in to the Jewish neighborhood, too.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In other words, to be together, all the Jews to be in one section.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And-- and I never heard the word ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's what happened, the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they gave us a little piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
